    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like everything is so heavy. if the character tries to fight it, they just suffer more, right? like, the more they cling to existence, the more it hurts to watch them fade. wouldn't it actually be more kind to just... tell them it's okay to let go? to tell them that it's actually okay to not want to exist anymore?",
